        <div class="journal_image right_image"><img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1171/4544/files/vogue-spy.png?994769845205606128" alt="journal image" /></div>
        <div class="journal_text left_text"><span class="heading_journal_section heading_footer">JOURNAL</span>
